From: filamind <abdelmonemawad@hotmail.com>
Subject: [PATCH 3/4] iot_drivers: tabbed ServerDialog with URL + pairing-code

Replaces the single ''Server token'' field with a tabbed dialog offering
two equivalent paths:
  * ''Server URL''     -- paste a bare https URL plus an optional 8-char
                          pairing code generated by the filamind-iot addon
                          (https://github.com/filamind-app/filamind-iot)
  * ''Pairing Token''  -- paste the full token from the IoT app (upstream)

The submit button calls /iot_drivers/connect_to_server with either
{url, code} or {token} depending on the active tab. The backend (patch 2)
performs the round-trip to /filamind_iot/pair when a code is supplied.

---
